scopes.name: schedule_only
scopes.explanation: Lines 3 to 127 comprise the entire Schedule to the 2002 ISDA Master Agreement, including all its Parts and provisions, and exclude any standard pre-printed text or CSA annexes. The text starts with the heading 'SCHEDULE' and ends with the execution blocks, which is typical for an ISDA Schedule. All content within this span is part of the Schedule.
